{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01JUSxET6WxJtS5CUYxvqf1w","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# F24 Plan\n2\t\n3\t## Acceptance criteria\n4\t\n5\tFrom SPEC.md §7.4 — Funnels (`/funnels`):\n6\t\n7\t- Step builder: ordered list of event name selectors (2–5 steps, add/remove buttons)\n8\t- Date range selector (same presets as Trends: Last 7d, Last 30d, Last 90d + custom date picker)\n9\t- Result: horizontal funnel bar chart showing user count per step, with conversion % annotations\n10\t- Drop-off percentage highlighted in red between steps\n11\t\n12\tFrom SPEC.md §6.5 — POST /api/funnels (already built in F12):\n13\t\n14\t- Body: `{ steps, start, end }` — 2–5 event name strings, ISO date range\n15\t- Response: per-step counts and conversion rates (`users`, `conversion_from_prev`, `conversion_overall`)\n16\t\n17\t## Dependencies\n18\t\n19\tCompleted features this builds on:\n20\t\n21\t- **F8** (`GET /api/schema`) — provides event name autocomplete list\n22\t- **F9** (`src/lib/schema-cache.ts`) — schema types\n23\t- **F12** (`POST /api/funnels` + `src/lib/funnels.ts`) — backend API route + query logic\n24\t- **F18** (layout shell + sidebar) — navigation already includes Funnels link\n25\t\n26\tExact file paths imported or extended:\n27\t\n28\t- `src/app/funnels/page.tsx` — MODIFY (currently a placeholder)\n29\t- `src/app/api/funnels/route.ts` — EXISTS, no changes needed\n30\t- `src/lib/funnels.ts` — EXISTS, types imported (`FunnelResponse`, `FunnelStepResult`)\n31\t- `src/lib/schema-cache.ts` — EXISTS, types imported (`SchemaResponse`)\n32\t\n33\t## Files to create or modify\n34\t\n35\t- CREATE `src/components/funnels/useFunnels.ts` — client-side hook: schema fetch, step state, date range state, POST to `/api/funnels`, response state\n36\t- CREATE `src/components/funnels/StepBuilder.tsx` — ordered list of Autocomplete selectors with add/remove buttons (2–5 steps)\n37\t- CREATE `src/components/funnels/FunnelDateRange.tsx` — date range controls (preset chips + custom date pickers), same pattern as TrendsControls\n38\t- CREATE `src/components/FunnelChart.tsx` — horizontal bar chart with Recharts `BarChart` (horizontal layout), user counts, conversion % annotations, red drop-off highlights\n39\t- MODIFY `src/app/funnels/page.tsx` — wire up `useFunnels` hook, `StepBuilder`, `FunnelDateRange`, and `FunnelChart`\n40\t- CREATE `src/components/funnels/__tests__/useFunnels.test.ts` — unit tests for the hook\n41\t- CREATE `src/components/funnels/__tests__/StepBuilder.test.tsx` — unit tests for step builder logic\n42\t- CREATE `src/components/__tests__/FunnelChart.test.tsx` — unit tests for funnel chart\n43\t\n44\t## Implementation order\n45\t\n46\t1. **Create `src/components/funnels/useFunnels.ts`** — hook managing: schema fetch from `/api/schema`, steps array state (default 2 empty strings), date range state (default last 30 days), `addStep`/`removeStep`/`setStep` helpers, POST to `/api/funnels` when steps are valid and date range is set, loading/error/result state.\n47\t\n48\t2. **Create `src/components/funnels/StepBuilder.tsx`** — renders an ordered list of MUI Autocomplete inputs populated from schema event names. Each row: step number label, Autocomplete, remove button (disabled when 2 steps). Add Step button at bottom (disabled when 5 steps). Receives steps array, event names, and setters as props.\n49\t\n50\t3. **Create `src/components/funnels/FunnelDateRange.tsx`** — preset chips (Last 7d, Last 30d, Last 90d) + two date inputs (Start, End). Same pattern as the date range section in `TrendsControls`. Receives `startDate`, `endDate`, and setters as props.\n51\t\n52\t4. **Create `src/components/FunnelChart.tsx`** — horizontal bar chart using Recharts `BarChart` with `layout=\"vertical\"`. Shows one bar per funnel step, bar width proportional to user count. Annotations: user count on each bar, conversion_from_prev percentage between bars, conversion_overall. Drop-off percentage (1 − conversion_from_prev) highlighted in red text between steps. Loading skeleton and empty state.\n53\t\n54\t5. **Modify `src/app/funnels/page.tsx`** — make it a `\"use client\"` page. Wire `useFunnels` hook, render `StepBuilder`, `FunnelDateRange`, a Run Funnel button, and `FunnelChart` with results.\n55\t\n56\t6. **Create unit tests** — `useFunnels.test.ts`, `StepBuilder.test.tsx`, `FunnelChart.test.tsx`.\n57\t\n58\t## Sprint contract\n59\t\n60\t- [ ] `pnpm test` → 0 failures\n61\t- [ ] `pnpm lint` → exit 0\n62\t- [ ] `pnpm typecheck` → exit 0\n63\t- [ ] `pnpm build` → exit 0\n64\t- [ ] File `src/components/funnels/useFunnels.ts` exists and exports `useFunnels`\n65\t- [ ] File `src/components/funnels/StepBuilder.tsx` exists and exports `StepBuilder`\n66\t- [ ] File `src/components/funnels/FunnelDateRange.tsx` exists and exports `FunnelDateRange`\n67\t- [ ] File `src/components/FunnelChart.tsx` exists and exports `FunnelChart`\n68\t- [ ] File `src/app/funnels/page.tsx` contains `\"use client\"` and imports `useFunnels`\n69\t- [ ] HTTP check: GET `http://localhost:3000/funnels` contains `data-testid=\"step-builder\"`\n70\t- [ ] HTTP check: GET `http://localhost:3000/funnels` contains `data-testid=\"funnel-date-range\"`\n71\t- [ ] HTTP check: GET `http://localhost:3000/funnels` contains `data-testid=\"funnel-chart\"`\n72\t\n73\t## Test plan\n74\t\n75\t- **Test file**: `src/components/funnels/__tests__/useFunnels.test.ts`\n76\t- **Module under test**: `useFunnels` hook\n77\t- **Cases to cover**:\n78\t  - Initial state has 2 empty steps, default date range (last 30 days), null result\n79\t  - `addStep` appends a step (up to 5 max)\n80\t  - `addStep` is a no-op when already at 5 steps\n81\t  - `removeStep` removes a step by index (minimum 2)\n82\t  - `removeStep` is a no-op when at 2 steps\n83\t  - `setStep` updates a step at a given index\n84\t  - Does not fetch funnel when fewer than 2 steps have non-empty values\n85\t  - Fetches funnel (POST /api/funnels) when all steps are non-empty 